## Test cases (all in-memory, no filesystem)
1. `dispatches_status_when_event_is_active` — active event → setter called
2. `skips_inactive_events` — future event → setter not called
3. `applies_transforms_in_priority_order` — two rules match; higher-priority
   rule's setter params win
4. `first_matching_transform_wins_per_setter` — two transforms in one rule;
   only first match dispatched
5. `continues_after_getter_error` — getter returns error on tick 1, events on
   tick 2; setter called on tick 2
6. `stops_on_context_cancel` — cancel ctx → Run returns promptly
7. `new_returns_error_for_missing_getter` — getter name not registered
8. `new_returns_error_for_missing_setter` — setter name not registered

